dct_description_sm: Cartographic Details: Scale [1: 1,600,000]. Imprint derived from the atlas in which the map was issued. Inset maps: "Iceland" ; "Feroe Islands." "Eng. by W. Dassauville ... " Shows boundaries, rivers and principal settlements. Greenwich meridian. Dimensions: 1 map ; 52 x 60 centimeters
dct_publisher_sm: Drawn & engraved for Thomson's New General Atlas (Edinburgh), 1814
